fix(watch): generic auth via --auth-user config flag + adapter.ensureAuth(user)

- ensureAuth() now takes optional preferredUser parameter
- Added --auth-user CLI flag and authUser config option
- GitHubAdapter: uses preferredUser if provided, falls back to URL-based detection
- AzureDevOpsAdapter: uses preferredOrg if provided, falls back to URL-based detection
- Removed all hardcoded usernames from watch code
- Tier 2 remediation now uses config.authUser via adapter

Usage: squad watch --execute --auth-user tamirdresher_microsoft
Or in config: { "watch": { "authUser": "tamirdresher_microsoft" } }

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
